info.name: Organization Admin
info.description: Top-level DataHub administrator. Has ALL privileges.

info.name: Access Admin
info.description: Able to manage users (including resetting passwords for native users) and groups. Can also edit policies and access tokens.

info.name: Metadata Steward
info.description: Able to both read and modify all assets across DataHub. Cannot make changes to users, group, policies and credentials.

info.name: Metadata Reader
info.description: Able to read metadata, but cannot change it by default (unless they are an owner of an asset).
